description: Northeast Portland's premier hot dog truck, Big Fat Weiners is a big fat winner! If you're looking for the best hot dogs and sausages in Portland then this is the truck you've been dreaming of. With genuine Hebrew National hot dogs and their own homemade sausages for your dining pleasure, Big Fat Weiners is bringing you the very best in quality, flavor, and service you'll absolutely love!
name: Big Fat Weiners
